metadata.name: Girl Scout Cookies #1/50
metadata.description:
It's cookie season! And to sweeten the deal, we're offering a special promotion: with every purchase, you'll be eligible to redeem one box of delicious cookies. These mouth-watering treats are the perfect complement to your cookie order, and they're sure to be a hit with everyone in your family. Plus, shipping is included within the continental US, so there's no extra cost to you!

Every valid claim is eligible to redeem one box of cookies, plus shipping within the continental United States. By submitting a claim, you acknowledge and agree to these terms of service.

*** Please contact AndrewFoord.eth | Grand Maestro#3041 on Discord for all information!***
